# Implementation Plan - Headphone Detection & Spatial Audio Guard

This plan implements real-time detection of headphones (wired or Bluetooth A2DP) to gated the Spatial Audio feature. This ensures a consistent user experience by preventing binaural effects on speakers or car audio systems.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Gating Logic**: Spatial Audio will be automatically "muted" at the DSP level if headphones are disconnected, even if the user has the toggle "ON".
> **UI Interaction**: The Spatial Audio card will be semi-transparent and non-expandable when headphones are not detected, with a clear "Headphones Required" message.

## Proposed Changes

