## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
- **Wired Headset**: Plug in 3.5mm jack. Verify Spatial Audio card enables immediately.
- **Bluetooth A2DP**: Connect Bluetooth headphones. Verify Spatial Audio card enables.
- **USB Headset**: Connect Type-C headphones. Verify Spatial Audio card enables.
- **Speaker Mode**: Disconnect all peripherals. Verify Spatial Audio card is greyed out.
- **App Start**: Launch app with headphones already connected vs. disconnected. Verify correct initial state.
- **Real-time Toggle**: Connect/disconnect while music is playing. Ensure audio effects update instantly.
